<div class="section">
  <h1>Supported Platforms</h1>

  <p><em>What platforms are supported?</em></p>

  <p>Most Android and iOS devices, including both phones and tablets (as well as
  other compatible devices, e.g., iPod Touch, but not including Android TV
  devices or watches and the like).</p>

  <p><em>Can I play the iPad version on my iPhone and vice-versa?</em></p>

  <p>Elexi will be universal, so will be able to be played on either type of
  device with one purchase.</p>

  <p><em>Will Elexi be available on any other platforms?</em></p>

  <p>No, there are no plans for any other platforms at this
  time.</p>

</div>
